item.title: Need help with my server (portforwarding pursay)
item.dc:creator: @Digital_Hotdogs Digital Hotdogs
item.description:
@Digital_Hotdogs wrote:

[quote=“coolpup2233, post:1, topic:259284”]this is not advertising
u may get a reward if u can get on.[/quote]

  1. If it’s not advertising, how come you’re giving out your server details to log in?
  2. I don’t think you’re allowed to offer rewards on these forums to get people on your server
  3. Next time use a server status page, if it doesn’t add, then it’s offline.
  4. Get someone on MSN to check instead of posting and causing hundreds to view the topic.
